    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a dependable choice for someone prioritizing function over form. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor dings, and fading paint on the roof. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and the driver's seat shows significant wear, though all essential electronics and climate controls remain operational. While it runs and drives reliably, it will likely require some minor maintenance in the near future to keep it in top shape. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for a budget-friendly daily driver.",
