    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver is this E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example has been mechanically optimized with a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and proactive rear subframe reinforcement. The drivetrain remains tight, utilizing a 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential to ensure maximum power delivery. Upgraded with Bilstein dampers for enhanced lateral stability and compression damping, this chassis provides a communicative, analog feedback loop. While the exterior shows minor patina indicative of a well-enjoyed driver, the powertrain and suspension geometry are sorted for immediate performance use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
