    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the ideal balance of performance and practicality for a driver who appreciates a well-maintained machine. The exterior retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and a small scuff on the rear passenger wheel\u2014typical of careful use but nothing that detracts from its overall presence. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and has never been smoked in; the leather seats show only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster, and all interior electronics, including the premium sound system and navigation, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health, having recently undergone a full inspection, synthetic oil change, and brake pad replacement. It has been garage-kept and comes with a comprehensive folder of service records dating back to its original purchase. This is a turn-key vehicle ready for its next chapter, offering a refined driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
